'''Afrika''' ke [[Lefasana|lefasana]] la bobedi ka bogolo lefaseng ge go lebelelwa sekgoba le badudi, lefasana la pele ka bogolo ke [[Asia|Asia]].

Bophara bja Afrika ekaba 6.0% bja lefase goba 20.4% bja naga ya lefase (ntle le mawatle)&nbsp;<ref name=Sayre>Sayre, April Pulley: ''Africa'', Twenty-First Century Books, 1999{{–}} ISBN 0-7613-1367-2.</ref> Afrika enale badudi bao ekabago 900,000,000 (go ya ka palo ya ngwaga wa 2005)&nbsp;<ref>[http://library.stanford.edu/africa/religion.html "World Population Prospects: The 2004 Revision"] [[United Nations]] (Department of Economic and Social Affairs, population division).</ref> ba elego 14% ya badudi ba lefase bophara.

Lefasana le le dikaneditšwe ke [[Mediterranean Sea|Mediterranean Sea]] go ya lebowa, [[Suez Canal|Suez Canal]] le [[Red Sea|Red Sea]] go ya lebowa bohlaba, [[Indian Ocean|Indian Ocean]] go ya borwa bohlaba, le [[Atlantic Ocean|Atlantic Ocean]] go ya bodikela.
Afrika e na le dinaga tše masomenne le metšo e tsheletšego (46) go akaretša Madagascar, boga tše masomehlano le metšo e meraro (53) ge go akarêtšwa dihlakahlake.

Afrika, bogareng [[Afrika Bohlabela|Afrika Bohlabela]], e tsebega ka bothomo bja bophelo baithuting ba thutamahlale.

